Class ApplicationServletOutputSteam

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • javax.servlet.ServletOutputStream
        • com.rockagen.malen.connector.ApplicationServletOutputSteam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class ApplicationServletOutputSteam
extends javax.servlet.ServletOutputStream
    ServletOutputStream override

    notice: this OutputServletStream is use BufferedOutputStream implements
    #write(int) must be flush after write , because,at RequestDispatcher ,we will call outputstream,if not flush , the headers and file maybe buffer,so ,we need flush after writer(b)
